Package: logitmp
Type: Package
Title: logistic model performance
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-09-29
Author: Frederik Sachser
Maintainer: <f.sachser@gmx.at>
Description: The package contains a function that computes several performance measures for logistic regression models. Furthermore it creates a ROC-plot and a calibration-plot. There are several options to customize the output. The function will install and attach the packages 'ResourceSelection' (for hoslem.test) and 'pROC' (for AUC and ROC-plot). If attached the package 'fmsb' will be detached.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: ResourceSelection, pROC, fmsb
